{"article_id":"xUeKBa6aG2zWkRyM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In his first interview","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"since being fired ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"former FBI Director James Comey described President Trump as an ego-driven liar","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"who treats women like \" meat \"","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and is \" morally unfit to be president . \"","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"he ' s medically unfit to be president .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"I think","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"he ' s morally unfit to be president , \"","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Comey said in a wide-ranging sit-down Sunday night with ABC News ' George Stephanopoulos .","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"\" A person","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"who sees moral equivalence in Charlottesville ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"who talks about and treats women","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"like they ' re pieces of meat ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"who lies constantly about matters big and small","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and insists","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"the American people believe him -","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that person is not fit to be president of the United States on moral grounds . \"","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"Ahead of the interview , Trump fired off a series of tweets","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"calling the country ' s former top cop a \" slimeball , \" a liar","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"and directly refuted claims","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"he asked Comey for his loyalty .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"During Sunday ' s televised interview , Comey also weighed in on the salacious","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"- and unverified -","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Russian dossier , as well as his reason","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"for going public about the probe into Hillary Clinton ' s private email server in the final days of the 2016 election .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"Clinton","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"as well as a large number of Democrats - have blamed her November defeat on Comey ' s actions .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"I hope not","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"but the honest answer is ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"t wouldn ' t have changed the way","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"think about it , \"","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"omey said .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"e added","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"e hoped","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"eople would read his book \" A Higher Loyalty \"","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"nd put themselves in his shoes .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"omey claimed","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"e wasn ' t trying to favor one candidate over the other","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"ut instead tried to do \" the right thing , \"","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"hough he admitted","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"is decision was influenced by the assumption","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"linton would beat Trump in the election .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"I don ' t remember spelling it out ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"ut it had to have been ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"hat she ' s going to be elected president","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"nd","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"f I hide this from the American people ,","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"he ' ll be illegitimate the moment","depth":16},{"id":49,"text":"he ' s elected ,","depth":16},{"id":50,"text":"he moment","depth":16},{"id":51,"text":"his comes out , \"","depth":16},{"id":52,"text":"e told Stephanopoulos .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"omey , though , seemed to be aware of the weight of his action .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"I walked around vaguely sick to my stomach ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"eeling beaten down , \"","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"e said .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"I felt like","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"was totally alone ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"hat everybody hated me .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"nd that there wasn ' t a way out","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"ecause it really was the right thing","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"o do . \"","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"omey also recounted his initial interactions with Trump over the unverified 35-page Russian dossier","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"hat was compiled by former British Intelligence officer Christopher Steele","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"nd funded in part by the Democratic National Committee and Clinton ' s campaign .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"he dossier detailed a graphic account of Trump with Russian prostitutes during a 2013 trip to Moscow .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"I ' m about to meet with a person","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"ho doesn ' t know me ,","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"ho ' s just been elected president of the United States...","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"rom my watching him during the ...","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"ampaign could be volatile , \"","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"omey said .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"And I ' m about to talk to him about allegations","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"hat he was involved with prostitutes in Moscow","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"nd that the Russians taped it","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"nd have leverage over him . \"","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"omey claimed","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"uring a Jan. 27 , 2017 private dinner meeting , Trump asked him to disprove the allegations in the dossier .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"He said ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"ou know ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"If there ' s even a 1 percent chance","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"y wife thinks","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"hat ' s true ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"hat ' s terrible . \"","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"omey added ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"' I remember thinking ,","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"How could your wife think","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"here 's a 1 percent chance","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"ou were with prostitutes","depth":17},{"id":90,"text":"eeing on each other in Moscow ? '","depth":17},{"id":91,"text":"'m a flawed human being ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"ut there is literally zero chance","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"hat my wife would think","depth":16},{"id":94,"text":"hat was true .","depth":16},{"id":95,"text":"o , what kind of marriage to what kind of man does your wife think","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"that ] there 's only a 99 percent chance","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"ou did n't do that ? \"","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"omey said","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"rump told him ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"I may order you to investigate that . \"","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"e allegedly advised the president","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"o \" be careful about that","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"ecause it might create a narrative","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"hat we ' re investigating you personally ,","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"nd second , it ' s very difficult to prove something didn ' t happen . \"","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"omey ' s interview with Stephanopoulos is part of a big media blitz","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"esigned to promote his book .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"n released excerpts , Comey compares Trump to a mafia boss","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"nd questions","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"hy the president initially refused to acknowledge","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"ussia meddled in the 2016 presidential election .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"e also takes aim at Trump ' s physical appearance ,","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"escribing him as \" slightly orange , with bright white half-moons under his eyes","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"here I assumed","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"e placed small tanning goggles . \"","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"he White House has worked hard in recent weeks","depth":4},{"id":117,"text":"o discredit Comey .","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"rump tweeted Sunday","depth":4},{"id":119,"text":"hat Comey was the \" WORST FBI Director in history , by far ! , \"","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"uggested","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"e should be behind bars","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"nd referred to him as \" a man","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"ho always ends up badly and out of whack","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"he is not smart ! ) . \"","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"n 1996 , Comey served as assistant U.S. Attorney for the Eastern District of Virginia during President Bill Clinton ' s administration .","depth":4},{"id":126,"text":"n 2002 , he was named U.S. Attorney for the Southern District of New York under President George W. Bush .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"n that role , he secured high-profile convictions","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"ncluding one against Martha Stewart for securities fraud , conspiracy and obstruction of justice .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"decade later , Comey was appointed by President Barack Obama","depth":6},{"id":130,"text":"nd confirmed 93-1 by the Senate as FBI director .","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"n Friday , White House Press Secretary Sarah Sanders called Comey ' s credibility into question .","depth":4},{"id":132,"text":"This is nothing more than a poorly executed PR stunt by Comey","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"o desperately rehabilitate his tattered reputation","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"nd enrich his own bank account","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"y peddling a book","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"hat belongs in the bargain bin of the fiction section , \"","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"he said .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":275,"left":253,"right":274,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":253,"left":155,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":147,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":142,"right":146,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":139,"right":141,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuc